{"tid":1795160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大罷工持續 馬克龍籲聖誕「休戰」","createTime":"2019-12-23T16:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T16:34:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"29b1716737d43e4c8bc0ff1df164607a05213916","tid":1795160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191223/645CXJRNG6A2ASI7LGPCG6BD3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191223%2F645CXJRNG6A2ASI7LGPCG6BD3E%2F&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=b85067af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191223%2F645CXJRNG6A2ASI7LGPCG6BD3E%2F&h=3d9472ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191223/645CXJRNG6A2ASI7LGPCG6BD3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n大罷工持續 馬克龍籲聖誕「休戰」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191223/large/1577028116_a56b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577028116_a56b.gif&h=e853afdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國總統馬克龍呼籲工會在聖誕期間暫停罷工。<br />\n<br />\n聖誕長假前日展開，惟反對退休金改革的法國大罷工至今仍未平息。總統馬克龍呼籲工會於聖誕假期間暫停罷工，以免趁假日出門的乘客行程受阻。<br />\n<br />\n正外訪科特迪瓦的馬克龍說：「罷工受憲法保護且有充份理由。不過我認為出於對家庭生活的尊重，有時候全國休戰也是好事。」他指暫停工業行動不但不代表工會放棄訴求，更顯示對想與親朋好友團聚的法國人的尊重和責任感。<br />\n<br />\n工會領袖與政府上周談判仍未能打破僵局，雖然部份工會都呼籲在節日期間暫停罷工，但仍有數個鐵路工人組織堅持繼續工業行動。工會期望能重現1995年一幕，聖誕前連續三周的鐵路罷工成功讓政府撤回退休金改革方案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首都一半地鐵停駛<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「伯利恒之疤」Banksy嘲以國建牆欺巴人<br />\n<br />\n巴黎一半地鐵線停駛。巴黎大眾運輸公司（RATP）指只有兩條無人駕駛的行車線維持運作。法國國鐵（SNCF）前日繼續縮減班次，高速列車TGV只維持平日的一半班次，未能按原定計劃讓全數85萬名持票乘客使用服務，警告交通將「嚴重受阻」。有打算從北部回到南部家鄉的乘客直言「無法忍受」罷工，感到沮喪，指「政府必須採取行動」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"952cf6efb4deeeaced20de0e95563c883f04a7a9","tid":1795160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">X&rsquo;MAS EVE 願平安歸香港🇭🇰</span><br />\n日期 : 12月24日 (二)<br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：<br />\n元朗yoho<br />\n沙田 新城市<br />\n尖沙咀 海港城<br />\n旺角 朗豪坊<br />\n銅鑼灣 時代廣場<br />\nLink : @xmasevehkchannel"},{"pid":"2f32d6bd109f653acf55f21188e0a32395812237","tid":1795160,"uid":3522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"法國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540ef69ac11a209066b51e0985f23f2e835edd12","tid":1795160,"uid":30247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"大罷工緊 佢仲得閒去非洲出訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常唔係提早返去處理咩"},{"pid":"5ccac273e4c74118bb4980bd2fef8a69eee755c5","tid":1795160,"uid":112241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"忽上腦？打架唔準打面？定係打架唔準用四肢？"},{"pid":"e8aacd286116fec606070043d7af4b640646ce17","tid":1795160,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"記得好似香港都話搞聖誕罷工 <br />\n後來又無左回事"},{"pid":"8c043b6d1de55b99a41fa48c3c5ee5e818e629a1","tid":1795160,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccac273e4c74118bb4980bd2fef8a69eee755c5","tid":1795160,"uid":112241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"忽上腦？打架唔準打面？定係打架唔準用四肢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"以前二戰都休戰，傳統黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c46a0a1dfeed30fc9f2ffe96c26e839bf0e35f","tid":1795160,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">休你老母</span></span>"}]}